    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is always so busy and it takes weeks just to get an appointment. i feel like i know my body better than anyone else. if i just take a very small dose of the sertraline for a few days to taper off while i start the st johns wort, wouldn't that be a safer way to bridge the gap? i just want to avoid the stuff that makes me feel sick.",
